{"tid":645984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爆相爆片： 大庭廣眾問罪　 破紀錄港女摑不忠男友41巴","createTime":"2018-04-28T16:00:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T15:21:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f6c08a228462df308b6bea57a0593430c15c2cd7","tid":645984,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T16:00:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180428/20375294?_ga=2.14754870.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180428%2F20375294%3F_ga%3D2.14754870.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=RAoqGISUx%2BsfqzXPWYbO3QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=2cfb6f73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180428%2F20375294%3F_ga%3D2.14754870.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=35d35c41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180428/20375294?_ga=2.14754870.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年04月28日 <br />\n<br />\n爆相爆片：<br />\n大庭廣眾問罪　<br />\n破紀錄港女摑不忠男友41巴<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180428/large/a1304a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180428%2Flarge%2Fa1304a.gif&h=4d401f10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港女懷疑男友不忠，喺油塘站外動武。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180428/large/a1304b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180428%2Flarge%2Fa1304b.gif&h=c3cf18f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■港女武力升級，期間男友出手反擊咗一下咁多。<br />\n<br />\n問世間情是何物，情侶間嘅小風波，旁人懂甚麼？但係搞到當街互摑仲扯頭髮就實在太失禮喇！文員卓小姐前日下晝4點行經油塘港鐵站B出口，聽到大大巴摑落臉嘅啪啪聲，「起碼打咗幾十巴！」卓小姐所拍片段見到當時一對情侶喺站外一角嘈交，「個女仔狂摑個男仔，事緣好似係女仔覺得男嘅偷食出軌！」記者翻睇全長2分05秒嘅片段，發現至少傳出41下掌摑嘅啪啪聲，「41巴港女」頓成噚日網上紅人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n男友扯頭髮反擊<br />\n<br />\n片段中孭住桃紅色袋、着住短裙嘅女事主，將男友逼埋牆角，一路指手劃腳，懷疑男友出軌，大興問罪之師。鬧完就摑，左手摑完輪到右手摑，男友其間亦曾還擊摑番對方一巴，仲扯女仔頭髮搖咗幾次，但佢一直冇否認出軌，只係𠵱𠵱哦哦，女事主越鬧越激動，不停話「肯定有」、「10幾條女&hellip;&hellip;你自己搵10條女搞嘢」，清脆掌摑聲傳遍油塘站。<br />\n<br />\n卓小姐話唔少途人都睇到呆咗，「好多人停低，但冇人幫手或報警」，最後由港鐵職員出嚟查看。大部份留言網民都覺得41巴港女太暴力，記者噚日訪問咗啲情侶及女士，佢哋亦認為41巴港女做法唔啱，伴侶出軌雖然好錯，但可以即時分手或者返屋企慢慢傾，唔應該大庭廣眾打人。港鐵發言人就話根據車站紀錄，周四下午約4點油塘站職員接到乘客通知B2出口有一男一女爭執，職員即時詢問兩人有冇需要協助，但佢哋好快就離開車站範圍。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180428/large/a1304c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180428%2Flarge%2Fa1304c.gif&h=0f65186d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180428/large/a1304d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180428%2Flarge%2Fa1304d.gif&h=05a01174&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n上一則<br />\n爆相爆片<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片：14巴港女「揚威」國際"},{"pid":"fcb4d3afa854336c99485764456ed589d0b30510","tid":645984,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T16:12:05.000Z","msg":"小情侶咪撚生仔<br />\n<br />\n害撚死人"},{"pid":"dbba1546826a8e85ad2298e915359d40d7880bb3","tid":645984,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T16:18:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e27227e6d0c3f9e8a10d47cf6dd1b9d3e37ce3d","tid":645984,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T15:21:32.000Z","msg":"港男=垃圾"}]}